     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXArr
      ** Error message data array (<ErrArrMax> x 45A, returned to caller)
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXArr
      ** Risk Factor Value in numeric format
     C                   PARM                    ##RSKF
 
      ** Parameters received from caller
      ** -------------------------------
      ** Risk Factor Value (11A, from transaction)
     C                   PARM                    @PRSKF
 
